# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI Math Tutor — Environment Variables Example
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in your real API keys.
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# ⚠️  NEVER commit `.env` to version control — it is listed in .gitignore.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Google Gemini API Key (REQUIRED for LLM-based LaTeX conversion) ───────────
# Get your free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# After signing in with your Google account, click "Create API key".
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ── OpenAI API Key (OPTIONAL — only needed if you use the OpenAI LLM backend) ─
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here
